      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ON THE WHISPER (1) is a handy type who was well below best latest at Q Lakeside, finishing fourth (25.75) in a Grade 5. Generally fast into stride but was shuffled back from the tricky draw last time. Better than last start and worth following up. NEAME (8) was a last start winner (21.34) at Q Lakeside who is building a strong winning record. Has never missed the frame here from three starts. Some good form is emerging from his last run. One of the leading chances again. HE'S REGAL (7) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 0.8 lengths (25.32) at Q Lakeside. Harder here but expected to measure up. HARA'S MILENA (3) is in form and must include among the chances.",
